description: "Pitch Signal & Scroll: essays, reporting, op-eds, and smart takes on digital life."
---

<section>
  <div class="section-title">
    <div>
      <h3>Write for {{ site.title }}</h3>
      <p>Pitch us a story in 60 seconds</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card post" style="grid-column: span 7">
      <h4 style="margin-top:0">Pitch guidelines</h4>
      <p>
        We publish pieces that explain what the internet is <em>doing to people</em> — and what people are doing inside it.
        Strong angles, clear claims, lived experience, light reporting, and cultural critique all welcome.
      </p>
      <ul style="margin:12px 0 0; padding-left:18px; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px">
        <li>Lead with a clear thesis: what’s your argument?</li>
        <li>Tell us why it matters <strong>now</strong>.</li>
        <li>Include 2–3 bullet points for the structure.</li>
        <li>Optional: links to writing samples.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <form onsubmit="return false;">
        <div class="hint">This is a starter form (no backend). For launch: connect Netlify Forms or a Google Form.</div>
        <div style="display:grid; gap:10px; margin-top:10px">
          <input placeholder="Your name" />
          <input placeholder="Your email" />
          <input placeholder="Proposed title" />
          <textarea placeholder="One-sentence thesis + quick outline (2–3 bullets)"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-top:12px">
          <a class="btn" href="mailto:editor@signalandscroll.com?subject=Pitch%20for%20Signal%20%26%20Scroll&body=Title%3A%0AOne-sentence%20thesis%3A%0AWhy%20now%3A%0AOutline%20(2%E2%80%933%20bullets)%3A%0ALinks%20(optional)%3A%0A">Email your pitch</a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="/about/">Our mission</a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="card post" style="grid-column: span 5">
      <h4 style="margin-top:0">Partnerships</h4>
      <p>Want to sponsor the newsletter or partner on a series? We work with brands that actually help readers.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-top:12px">
        <a class="btn secondary" href="mailto:partners@signalandscroll.com?subject=Partnership%20inquiry">Contact partnerships</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hint">Replace these emails once you own your domain.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
